        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your ancestors, along with most izalguuns, left the Scoured Stars before the Gap to escape the influence of the god Kadrical. They then settled on a planet that later came to be known as Izalraan. Most izalguuns on Izalraan serve as laborers to provide for their people. In either case, a powerful bite from their formidable jaws is useful.</p>\n<p>You gain a jaws unarmed attack that deals 1d6 piercing damage, is in the brawling group, and has the finesse and unarmed traits.</p>"
